OL,3,CMan recalls moment boat capsized in
OL,4,Cstormy weather during Atlantic
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FA Wiltshire man has described "the
OL,8,Fbrutal, brutal environment" he's
OL,9,Fdealing with during an Atlantic rowing
OL,10,Fchallenge.
OL,12,FJohn Watling, from Lacock, is part of
OL,13,Fa team attempting what's been dubbed
OL,14,F'the world's toughest row' - from the
OL,15,FCanaries to Antigua.
OL,17,FJohn spoke to ITV News West Country
OL,18,Fover satellite phone on Thursday 3
OL,19,FJanuary, just days after they capsized
OL,20,Fduring bad weather.
