OL,3,CMan recalls moment boat capsized in
OL,4,Cstormy weather during Atlantic
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FAfter three weeks at sea, they're
OL,8,Fcurrently around 1,000 miles off the
OL,9,Fwest coast of Africa, with 1,700
OL,10,Fnautical miles to go.
OL,12,FHe said: "It was pretty tough. We got
OL,13,Fpushed into some bad weather. The boat
OL,14,Fgot completely swamped with the water
OL,15,Fand pushed sideways.
OL,17,F"We broke two oars. This was at night.
OL,18,FIt was pretty scary. We were in the
OL,19,Fbad weather for about 10 days.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
