OL,3,CMan recalls moment boat capsized in
OL,4,Cstormy weather during Atlantic
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"The waves were standing up vertically
OL,8,Fas they came at you. On the ninth
OL,9,Fnight, I think it was 4am, once again
OL,10,Fwe got pinned and then we heard the
OL,11,Fwave coming and it sounded like a
OL,12,Ftrain coming into a train station.
OL,14,F"I could sense what was gonna happen
OL,15,Fand it capsized us, came right over. I
OL,16,Ffelt the 'bubble, bubble, bubble' in
OL,17,Fmy ears as we went upside down. We
OL,18,Fcame back up straight away.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
