OL,3,CMan recalls moment boat capsized in
OL,4,Cstormy weather during Atlantic
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"Two of the lads on deck - Sam and
OL,8,FJason - both had fallen over the side,
OL,9,Fbut of course, they clipped on.
OL,11,F"The deck of the boat was completely
OL,12,Fstrewn. It was swamped with water."
OL,14,FJohn revealed water flooded the rear
OL,15,Fcabin, playing havoc with the
OL,16,Felectrics.
OL,18,FHe said: "It's been an absolute
OL,19,Fbattle. It's a brutal, brutal
OL,20,Fenvironment to be in but we're in good
OL,21,Fspirits and we're forging on."
