OL,3,CMan recalls moment boat capsized in
OL,4,Cstormy weather during Atlantic
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FDespite the turbulent journey, John
OL,8,Fsaid they're not giving up.
OL,10,FThey're on a routine of rowing for two
OL,11,Fhours and resting for two hours. This
OL,12,Fis for 24 hours a day, seven days a
OL,13,Fweek, for six weeks.
OL,15,FThe team has thanked friends and
OL,16,Ffamily at home.
OL,18,FJohn said: "It's just the support from
OL,19,Fback home and knowing everybody there
OL,20,Fis supporting us.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
