OL,3,CMan recalls moment boat capsized in
OL,4,Cstormy weather during Atlantic
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"Spirits are pretty high, but when the
OL,8,Fweather's died right down. The wind's
OL,9,Ffairly low at the moment, and we're
OL,10,Fwaiting for the final corridor of wind
OL,11,Fweather to push us on to Antigua.
OL,13,F"I just think all the boys - Sam,
OL,14,FNoel, Jason, and myself - would just
OL,15,Flike to thank our loved ones."
OL,17,FThe team is raising money for Lyme
OL,18,FDisease UK. John's 25-year-old
OL,19,Fdaughter Yasmin now has to spend hours
OL,20,Fon a drip every day after being bitten
OL,21,Fby a tick at the age of 19.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
