OL,7,FYasmin did not see the tick, but
OL,8,Fdiscovered an enormous red bullseye
OL,9,Frash on her leg and realised she may
OL,10,Fhave been infected with Lyme Disease.
OL,12,FIn the years since, Lyme disease has
OL,13,Fhad an enormous and negative impact on
OL,14,Fher life - leaving her with extreme
OL,15,Ffatigue, brain fog, memory loss and
OL,16,Fneck pain among other symptoms.
OL,18,FJohn said: "It's our honour and
OL,19,Fprivilege to be representing the
OL,20,Fcommunity of people that have chronic
OL,21,For long-term Lyme disease.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
